## 🧑🏾‍🏫 what this challenge teaches u
in some files the version is appended after the file's signature
there r situation in which u cannot write the raw bytes with the keyboard
the solution is to use a python script that it will fill those bytes for u
wb -> write binary. it means no conversions r done 
to write those bytes u have to import struct library and use the method pack:
- <I -> writes 4bytes in Little Endian
- <H -> writes 2bytes in Little Endian

